And I just kept thinking, there is no way for you to be able to climb every route in Moab.

00:33:03.938 --> 00:33:07.604
And Moab is just one tiny little aspect of everything that God's made.

00:33:08.666 --> 00:33:14.415
And so then I just start thinking like, goodness, so much creativity has gone into this, right?

00:33:14.455 --> 00:33:18.402
And this is just what God has, what he's created.

00:33:19.043 --> 00:33:30.482
We get to, for the rest of eternity, explore the heart and the personality of the one that has created the things that we are in love with adventuring through.

00:33:31.170 --> 00:33:32.472
for all of eternity.

00:33:32.512 --> 00:33:35.616
We get to explore the heart and the personality of the One.

00:33:35.836 --> 00:33:41.845
If He's made these things that great, and this is just something He made, what would it be like to get to know Him forever?

00:33:42.205 --> 00:33:46.171
The idea is that we would be full to bursting.

00:33:48.894 --> 00:34:00.210
If you've never given your heart to God, if you've never trusted in what God accomplished through the cross, I want to give you a chance to do that.

00:34:00.546 --> 00:34:01.367
It's so easy.

00:34:01.407 --> 00:34:04.391
You just, God says you just pray.

00:34:05.332 --> 00:34:16.587
You just believe in your heart that Jesus is God and you confess with your mouth that he was raised from the dead in order to transfer us from that domain of darkness into the kingdom of light.

00:34:17.648 --> 00:34:23.296
I might give you a chance to do that, but real quick, I want us to think about a question.

00:34:25.699 --> 00:34:28.082
I don't know if you have ever fed a small child.

00:34:29.090 --> 00:34:31.934
we have two children and they're not small anymore.

00:34:32.434 --> 00:34:45.190
But when they were small, you know, you get the little baby grubber food jars and you have your little plastic spoon, you know, and they're sitting in their high chair, they got their bib on, and you're, you know, shoving pureed turkey into their mouth, right?

00:34:46.071 --> 00:34:54.922
And it's going all over their face and you keep doing that and you're, you know, having conversations and eventually you take out a spoon and then you go and it's like brick wall.

00:34:55.323 --> 00:34:58.066
It's just not going in, right?

00:34:58.210 --> 00:34:59.952
And you ask the question, are you awful?

00:35:01.094 --> 00:35:01.915
You awful, right?

00:35:02.316 --> 00:35:06.782
Chris Gwinn, our campus pastor in Calispell, he says his daughter just smacks it out of the way.

00:35:07.743 --> 00:35:08.004
Boom.

00:35:08.044 --> 00:35:08.665
There's no brick wall.

00:35:08.685 --> 00:35:09.646
It's just, I'm done, right?

00:35:10.788 --> 00:35:11.849
Fiery little child.

00:35:12.510 --> 00:35:14.513
And so you ask the question, are you awful?

00:35:16.435 --> 00:35:26.930
And it's interesting because you see this theme in this passage, right, that we would be filled with the knowledge of his will in all spiritual wisdom, in all

00:35:27.138 --> 00:35:37.229
spiritual understanding, that we would experience the greatness of all of his power to have all endurance and all patience and joy.

00:35:40.693 --> 00:35:44.998
It begs the question, am I all full?

00:35:47.781 --> 00:35:48.442
Am I all full?

00:35:49.964 --> 00:35:50.705
Full to bursting.

00:35:51.946 --> 00:35:55.410
But I think it's kind of a misconstrued question because

00:35:56.514 --> 00:36:03.183
You can't be full to bursting unless you are filled with awe.

00:36:05.967 --> 00:36:23.410
You can't be full to bursting unless you can get on your knees and recognize the glorious might to power the infinite wisdom, the uncontainable majesty and glory of who God is.

00:36:24.866 --> 00:36:26.248
You don't have to do anything.

00:36:27.149 --> 00:36:28.350
It's all been done for you.

00:36:29.011 --> 00:36:30.172
All you have to do is just take it in.

00:36:31.654 --> 00:36:33.576
Be filled with all.

00:36:34.497 --> 00:36:36.619
Be filled with reverence.

00:36:38.341 --> 00:36:44.107
Be filled with mystery, curiosity, exploration.

00:36:48.572 --> 00:36:49.814
God wants to move in your heart.

00:36:50.715 --> 00:36:51.776
He wants to move in your life.

00:36:51.796 --> 00:36:53.778
He desires like a father

00:36:53.922 --> 00:36:57.807
reaching out to his son like a daughter reaching out to her father.

00:36:58.428 --> 00:37:04.655
He wants us to engage in this and so I would challenge you to stoke the passion of your heart for God.

00:37:05.396 --> 00:37:09.601
Get into his word and start understanding who he is.

00:37:09.641 --> 00:37:11.544
Investigate, ask the questions.

00:37:12.725 --> 00:37:21.135
Be paying attention to your life as you're living and look for God in all the intricate beautiful ways that he is involved in your life.

00:37:22.277 --> 00:37:23.218
I used to pray

00:37:24.322 --> 00:37:28.646
that God would allow me to see the spiritual world the way Neo sees the matrix.

00:37:30.148 --> 00:37:30.328
Right?

00:37:30.608 --> 00:37:36.854
There's that turning point in the matrix when all of a sudden, Neo looks up and he sees everything for what it actually is.

00:37:37.875 --> 00:37:45.923
And I would desperately pray, God, please, please let me see the spiritual realm like Neo sees the matrix.

00:37:46.583 --> 00:37:47.944
I just want that.

00:37:49.066 --> 00:37:51.268
And I was bummed because he wouldn't answer my prayer.

00:37:52.609 --> 00:37:53.810
He didn't allow me to see that.

00:37:56.322 --> 00:38:03.392
But then I realized, and this is a rhythm that we have as a church, while we're fasting.

00:38:03.432 --> 00:38:10.461
So every year, at the beginning of the year, we have this time that we separate to fast, to sacrifice something in order to seek God.

00:38:11.723 --> 00:38:13.485
And sometimes it's food, sometimes it's other things.

00:38:13.545 --> 00:38:14.086
It doesn't matter.

00:38:14.487 --> 00:38:16.770
We're letting go in order to seek God.

00:38:16.790 --> 00:38:23.679
And I noticed that when I'm fasting, I become more aware of what God is doing all around me.

00:38:24.540 --> 00:38:25.842
When I'm fasting,

00:38:26.146 --> 00:38:29.873
I actually see, wait, he's moving in a miraculous way over here.

00:38:30.414 --> 00:38:31.616
Wait a minute, I didn't see that before.

00:38:31.656 --> 00:38:34.882
He's actually growing and changing and challenging.

00:38:35.162 --> 00:38:39.891
Wait a minute, you take a step back and you see, oh my gosh, everything is happening.

00:38:39.911 --> 00:38:40.792
It's all unfolding.

00:38:40.832 --> 00:38:43.056
It's not the way that I imagined it like a movie.

00:38:43.076 --> 00:38:44.860
No, it was more practical than that.

00:38:45.481 --> 00:38:46.623
You can't see the spiritual.

00:38:46.683 --> 00:38:48.466
It's invisible.

00:38:48.770 --> 00:38:49.010
Right?

00:38:49.130 --> 00:38:50.452
But God enabled my heart to see it.

00:38:50.812 --> 00:38:51.673
I was aware.

00:38:51.693 --> 00:38:53.475
I was chasing after Him.

00:38:53.856 --> 00:39:00.223
And I had taken, I'd done everything I could to be able to become more aware through fasting and through prayer.

00:39:00.663 --> 00:39:01.424
So I would challenge you.

00:39:01.464 --> 00:39:02.025
Pay attention.

00:39:02.585 --> 00:39:03.767
Pay attention to what's going on.

00:39:03.947 --> 00:39:04.628
Seek God.

00:39:05.448 --> 00:39:09.052
Seek first His kingdom and all of these things will be added to you.

00:39:10.554 --> 00:39:10.935
Let's pray.

00:39:17.101 --> 00:39:17.682
Father,

00:39:19.554 --> 00:39:20.335
Thank you so much.

00:39:22.038 --> 00:39:23.620
Thank you for what you have done.

00:39:25.523 --> 00:39:29.409
One, in creating this marvel of where we live.

00:39:31.372 --> 00:39:36.059
Two, in being willing to step into that creation that you made.

00:39:37.281 --> 00:39:41.527
Three, in being willing to subject yourself to it.

00:39:42.949 --> 00:39:48.658
To the extent that you would give even your own life on the cross.

00:39:48.930 --> 00:39:52.614
that you would die, that you would go into the grave.

00:39:54.176 --> 00:40:15.639
God, thank you that in three days you would burst out of that grave conquering death forever and creating an opportunity for now me, for us to be able to stand in your presence forever and to drink and to taste and see that you are good so that our hearts would be satisfied and so that you would get glory.

00:40:17.281 --> 00:40:18.642
Thank you for rescuing us.

00:40:19.234 --> 00:40:33.569
I pray that through your Holy Spirit, you would so enlighten our hearts to see the ways that you're working and moving all that we would grow in wisdom, all spiritual wisdom.

00:40:34.090 --> 00:40:47.424
God, I pray that you would create a desire inside of a stoke of fire to get into your word and to understand who you are, to do it in community, to do it on our own, to just grow in our understanding.

00:40:48.165 --> 00:40:49.106
And I love

00:40:49.282 --> 00:40:55.892
God that we get to do that for all of eternity, all of eternity to explore the depths of who you are.

00:40:56.733 --> 00:41:00.239
Help us, God, to be full to bursting.

00:41:02.021 --> 00:41:09.513
And if you're here today, and you've never given God your life, you've never trusted your heart to Jesus.

00:41:10.274 --> 00:41:12.998
I told you earlier, I would give you the opportunity to do that.

00:41:13.499 --> 00:41:14.821
That opportunity is right now.

00:41:15.642 --> 00:41:18.066
If you want to give your heart to Jesus,

00:41:18.146 --> 00:41:19.768
It's as simple as praying a prayer.

00:41:20.248 --> 00:41:21.590
And I'm going to guide you through that.

00:41:21.610 --> 00:41:22.491
I'm going to pray this prayer.

00:41:22.511 --> 00:41:28.878
Our whole church is going to pray this prayer with you so that there's a sense of, we're in this with you, OK?

00:41:29.438 --> 00:41:30.379
I'm going to lead you in this prayer.

00:41:30.399 --> 00:41:37.827
And the thing is, this prayer isn't some magical, you know, there's no magical weight to it.

00:41:37.847 --> 00:41:45.055
It's just your heart and the position of your heart before God, you crying out to him, you reaching out to him, what you were made to do.

00:41:45.095 --> 00:41:47.538
And so that that's you in this moment.

00:41:47.650 --> 00:41:49.112
I would love you to lead you in that prayer.

00:41:49.932 --> 00:41:50.573
We could pray together.

00:41:50.593 --> 00:41:51.234
You could pray this.

00:41:53.196 --> 00:41:56.920
Say, dear God, thank you for loving me.

00:41:59.943 --> 00:42:08.452
Thank you for dying for me and rising from the dead in order to save my life.

00:42:10.894 --> 00:42:14.418
Thank you for transferring me from darkness into light.

00:42:17.858 --> 00:42:19.820
and giving me the hope to live for you.

00:42:22.664 --> 00:42:27.650
Fill me with your Holy Spirit and help me to be aware of you and everything.

00:42:30.194 --> 00:42:31.495
I give you my life.

00:42:33.177 --> 00:42:34.259
In Jesus' name I pray.

00:42:36.422 --> 00:42:43.090
With all our heads bowed and eyes closed, if that was you, and this is that moment that you just drew a line in the sand,

00:42:44.098 --> 00:42:45.259
You might not know everything.

00:42:45.319 --> 00:42:48.002
That's OK. You're closer than you were before, right?

00:42:48.463 --> 00:42:50.125
You don't need to have all the questions answered.

00:42:50.145 --> 00:42:51.186
You just drew that line.

00:42:51.226 --> 00:42:58.454
If that was you and you just made this decision to give your heart to God, would you just raise your hand up on the count of three?

00:42:58.754 --> 00:43:08.825
Just raise it up as a way of surrendering your heart to God to put a physical expression to a spiritual decision that you just made.

00:43:08.865 --> 00:43:11.008
So on the count of three, one, two, three.

00:43:11.048 --> 00:43:13.010
If that was you, raise up your hand.

00:43:14.114 --> 00:43:18.356
Come on, church, let's celebrate those who have made this decision.
